  "title": "Xtra Indulgent Mexican Muffin Chilaquiles",
  "description": "A winey and aerated Mexican dish featuring muffins and coconut cream, served in a bamboo tray. This indulgent Chiapan-inspired recipe is perfect for a Mediterranean-friendly meal.",
