  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350 degrees.",
    "Cut the muffins into 1-inch cubes and toast until lightly browned.",
    "In a large skillet, heat the coconut cream over medium heat.",
    "Add the red wine, chili peppers, onion, and garlic to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the toasted muffin cubes to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a bamboo tray and top with shredded cheese.",
    "Bake in the preheated oven for 10 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Remove from the oven and sprinkle with chopped cilantro, salt, and pepper.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
  ],
